Third-party components
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sparkle (https://sparkle-project.org)
  Auto-update framework. MIT License. Fetched as a Swift Package dependency at
  build time; not vendored in this repository.

Wine (https://www.winehq.org)
  GameMaster downloads a pre-built, open-source Wine runtime at first run.
  Wine is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License (LGPL) v2.1 or
  later. GameMaster does not modify or redistribute Wine within this repository;
  it downloads an unmodified upstream build and its source is available from the
  respective distributor. The default runtime is the community "Game Porting
  Toolkit" build maintained by Gcenx
  (https://github.com/Gcenx/game-porting-toolkit).

