Apple Game Porting Toolkit / D3DMetal
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

GameMaster does NOT bundle, redistribute, or re-host Apple's D3DMetal libraries
or any part of the Game Porting Toolkit "Evaluation environment for Windows
games". Those components are proprietary to Apple Inc. and are subject to
Apple's own license terms. When a user chooses to update their graphics layer,
GameMaster imports the libraries from a disk image the user obtains directly
from Apple; the libraries remain solely on the user's machine.

